            <description><![CDATA[朋友一起当然是打火锅最有气氛啦 <br> <br>【10.9】杨国福 牛油番茄火锅底料共550g <br> <br>拍25.9的选项就是这个价啦，有牛油、番茄口味的可以选都很好吃<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>而且挺大一包的，两包还是够三五个人吃的👌 <br> <br>平时不知道做什么的时候也可以拿来做麻辣烫啦、麻辣香锅都很不错哦真的跟店里的没什么差别<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0wjtav6kej20j60pkgoe.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0wjtbeviwj20j60pkjv1.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0wjtbyczpj20j60pk41g.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0wjtcgab8j20j60p9jtz.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0wjtd0pfsj20j60nvwhh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0wjtdhno7j20dy0dv3zn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0wjte1bzcj2010010gld.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
